headline: The Bull Market Continues: 1 Stock-Split Stock to Buy as Part of Your 2025 New Year's Resolution
summary: Companies can remedy that with a stock split, multiplying the number of shares they have in circulation while simultaneously reducing the stock price proportionately.  For example, a 10-for-1 stock split would increase a company's share count tenfold, and reduce its price-per-share to one-tenth of what it was previously.  Nvidia completed a 10-for-1 split on June 10 that reduced its stock price from $1,200 to around $120.
